outdoors, coaching, and playing sports; and
SJR105 INTRODUCED
85 WHEREAS, Lieutenant Governor Ainsworth will forever
86 be remembered for his conservative Christian values, ethical
87 standards, and staunch advocacy for jobs and high quality
88 public education; now therefore,
89 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, BOTH
90 HOUSES THEREOF CONCURRING, That Lieutenant Governor Will
91 Ainsworth is highly honored and commended for his many
92 contributions to the people of Alabama, and we express
93 profound gratitude for his dedicated service as a mentor,
94 role model, and advocate for the continued growth of
95 Alabama, inspiring others through his professionalism,
96 compassion, and tireless work ethic.
97 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, That this resolution be
98 entered into the official record as a lasting tribute to
99 Lieutenant Governor Will Ainsworth's exemplary leadership
100 and enduring impact on the residents of Alabama.
